OL,3,CTikToker, 20, in court over alleged
OL,4,Cposts showing terrorist attacks
OL,6,FA 20-year-old man has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with posting videos and
OL,8,Fimages of terrorist attacks on TikTok.
OL,10,FSardar Shahid, from Dudley, is charged
OL,11,Fwith four counts of distributing a
OL,12,Fterrorist publication between December
OL,13,F2024 and February 2025.
OL,15,FA 159-page document, titled Islamic
OL,16,FTerrorist Explosive Manual
OL,17,FTranslation, was found on a USB drive
OL,18,Fafter the 20 year old's arrest.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
