OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772291020
OL,3,CTikToker, 20, in court over alleged
OL,4,Cposts showing terrorist attacks
OL,6,FThe document contained details and
OL,7,Finstructions on how to build high
OL,8,Fexplosives.
OL,10,FMaterial was allegedly shared on
OL,11,FTikTok to encourage terrorism and
OL,12,Fincluded images of perpetrators of
OL,13,Fwell-known attacks, the court was told.
OL,15,FShahid appeared at the Old Bailey on
OL,16,FFriday for a preliminary hearing
OL,17,Fbefore Mrs Justice Cheema-Grubb.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
