OL,3,CTikToker, 20, in court over alleged
OL,4,Cposts showing terrorist attacks
OL,6,FThe defendant, who appeared by video
OL,7,Flink from Brinsford prison in
OL,8,FStaffordshire, spoke only to confirm
OL,9,Fhis identity.
OL,11,FThe defendant was remanded into
OL,12,Fcustody.
OL,14,FHe will enter a plea on July 3 and go
OL,15,Fon trial on March 15 next year at
OL,16,FBirmingham Crown Court.
